{"tid":661469,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"突發，古巨基演唱會途中跌落窿","createTime":"2018-05-11T14:49:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-11T15:31:36.000Z","uid":20430,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"146ca4f9e7a36d39ecd5019dfa2c8a69cdd31b43","tid":661469,"uid":20430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T14:49:29.000Z","msg":"古巨基一連五場《WE我們世界巡迴演唱會&mdash;香港站特別版》噚晚喺紅館開鑼，今日嚟到第二場，就有意外發生。今日古巨基開騷時同噚日一樣坐住時光機出場，唱完第一首歌《爆了》之後，佢就話：「有7年冇返紅館，比啲聲我聽！」點知講完呢句嘢，佢就跌咗落去台中間嘅一個窿，而呢個窿原本就係畀部時光機離開，但古巨基就唔小心跌咗落去。<br />\n<br />\n古巨基之後消失咗十幾分鐘，基仔再上台時就捽一捽後腦，仲話：「冇問題，係我錯，係我唔知道唔記得咗時光機個位，冇問題，多謝你哋願意係到等番我上來，我好想繼續落去 ，我盡力繼續落去，冇事，大家不用緊張，不用擔心，冇事，上天會保祐我，冇事。我行到係咪？講到邊到，我由頭來過啦。」講到「七年冇聽紅館聲音！」觀眾歡呼聲隨即四起，基仔好感動：「用最大努力演出，回報大家。暫時講咁多先，唱《必殺技》！」之後唱出《必殺技》，仲照舊喺台上踱步。其後基仔回到後台，如常更換舞衣，唱《歡樂今宵》時仲識講笑：「把聲仲靚咗！」基仔其後又喺台上話：「係背脊落地，唔係個頭，大家唔好擔心！不過一陣如果換衫位耐啲 ，跳舞硬啲！大家體諒下。」原來今晚基仔嘅父母都有嚟睇。<br />\n<br />\n英皇高層霍汶希回覆查詢時表示：「基仔喺升降台跌咗落去，但好彩係跌親，應該可能條頸有跌倒，我哋全部人過緊紅館睇佢，可能佢唱完歌要去醫院照一照，佢仲唱緊歌，傷勢唔係好重。」<br />\n<br />\n身為基仔好朋友嘅陳志雲噚晚去咗睇頭場，今晚志雲雖然唔喺現場，但基仔發生意外後已經第一時間知道，志雲啱啱同《蘋果》講：「我知道呀，我有朋友去睇，佢話俾我聽嗰陣嚇死我，嚇到我個心離一離，好在冇幾耐佢冇事上番台表演啦。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/11/224914_5ba874cc40277aeb3891c0ec990c6627.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F11%2F224914_5ba874cc40277aeb3891c0ec990c6627.png&h=d6eb618d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/11/224915_d86fc9c798af6916442a35657a1b25e1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F11%2F224915_d86fc9c798af6916442a35657a1b25e1.png&h=d80e806a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/11/224916_9a57dd4dc8ce63d214fcbf41cb4b7a48.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F11%2F224916_9a57dd4dc8ce63d214fcbf41cb4b7a48.png&h=87f70fef&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/11/224916_adda1252e8d86de8f5dcaa1ccfc4ad5c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F11%2F224916_adda1252e8d86de8f5dcaa1ccfc4ad5c.png&h=933f1a1f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/11/224917_adda1252e8d86de8f5dcaa1ccfc4ad5c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F11%2F224917_adda1252e8d86de8f5dcaa1ccfc4ad5c.png&h=7b288abe&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/11/224917_63ea72a3a3f5fbb1e20246951cb2b207.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F11%2F224917_63ea72a3a3f5fbb1e20246951cb2b207.png&h=57746c9c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/11/224918_63ea72a3a3f5fbb1e20246951cb2b207.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F11%2F224918_63ea72a3a3f5fbb1e20246951cb2b207.png&h=8ff90934&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/11/224919_1f2633c6d36bc9e9ab782cc0b28457c4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F11%2F224919_1f2633c6d36bc9e9ab782cc0b28457c4.png&h=13008ece&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"13b83b918a88994707f1070925230d928c112194","tid":661469,"uid":82398,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T14:53:24.000Z","msg":"好危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好再得罪人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d49a2fe98cbe22b433dc7466b8b938d32875fba2","tid":661469,"uid":29533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T14:5